      • main

        public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
                 throws java.io.IOException

        This is the main method from where execution will start It will call readSocioEconomicData and dispScioEconomicData to read the csv file. Then it display the options to user and calls dispScioEconomicData / dispBirthRate to display that processed data.

        The createAreaDataMapping is called to create mapping between area and the area data.

        PearsonsCorrelation is used to calculate correlation between teen birth rate and poverty as well as teen birth rate and education.
        Parameters:
        args - default parameter
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - If an input or output exception occured
